# Auto-HTTPS for the backend API only. The frontend (bezant.trade + app.bezant.trade)
# is served by Vercel. Requires a public DNS A record for api.bezant.trade pointing
# at this host (Cloudflare: DNS-only / grey cloud so Caddy can complete the ACME
# challenge directly), plus ports 80 + 443 open. Set your ACME contact email below.
{
	email admin@bezant.trade
}

api.bezant.trade {
	encode zstd gzip
	reverse_proxy backend:3001
}
